node.title: Three seriously injured after central city fight
node.description: Police are examining the scene in Auckland where a "serious altercation" left three people with serious injuries.
node.content:
["Police are examining the scene in Auckland where a "serious altercation" left three people with serious injuries.", "", "
File pic Photo: 123RF
", "Police say they were called to the incident at an address on Vincent St in the city's CBD around 4am.", "They are reviewing CCTV footage to identify those involved.", "All three people were taken to hospital."]
